CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 28, 2005

[Cite as 02/28/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-802.]

*1449MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2004-1765. State ex rel. Vindicator Printing Co. v. Youngstown.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus.

Upon consideration of relator’s motion to exceed page limitation in its merit brief,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and hereby is, granted.
